<br>
I disagree that dodger would be insignificant (especially if we could get evade 2).  Either way at high rr we could finally have some sort of viable defense with dodger without giving up our decent damage via 2H.<br>
<br>
I would also disagree with the minstrel side bar comments.  You can not under-estimate the power that a good minstrel twisting charm on a red con pet and ablative on you in a 1v1 fight.<br>
<br>
IMO a minstrel has a higher ceiling for effectiveness/power than a skald.  This does not make the skald bad, however.  Most people who play this game dont realize the power of multiple skalds.  IF you are on the /assist train and you get 2 or 3 skalds all on same target, its crazy.  That target (should ALWAYS be healing class/robed caster/musician) is dead before it can be healed with 4-6 DDs and three 2H weapon hits.  Thats at least (with 3 skalds) 900 DD damage and 500 weapon damage in 1-2 seconds.  Most robed casters are insta dead; healing classes/musicians soon will be as well.<br>
